trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pela instância atual do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar `Dispose` quando terminar de usar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O `Dispose` método deixa o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>em um estado inutilizável.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar `Dispose`, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>para o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>estava ocupando.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada `Dispose` antes de liberar sua última referência a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não serão liberados até que o coletor de lixo chame o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider"></xref> class and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider"> </xref> classe e, opcionalmente, libera os recursos gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>para liberar recursos gerenciados e não gerenciados; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> para liberar apenas recursos não gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: Gets all the exports that match the conditions of the specified import.
trans-unit.target: Obtém todas as exportações que correspondem às condições da importação especificada.

trans-unit.source: Implementers should not treat cardinality-related mismatches as errors and are not expected to throw exceptions in those cases.
trans-unit.target: Os implementadores não devem tratar incompatibilidades de cardinalidade como erros e não deverão gerar exceções nesses casos.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the import requests exactly one export and the provider has either no matching exports or more than one, the method should return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se a importação solicita exatamente uma exportação e o provedor tem nenhum exportações de correspondência ou em mais de um, o método deve retornar uma <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>coleção de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>

trans-unit.source: The conditions of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"></xref> objects to be returned.
trans-unit.target: As condições do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"> </xref> objetos a serem retornadas.

trans-unit.source: The transactional container for the composition.
trans-unit.target: O contêiner transacional para a composição.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains all the exports that match the specified condition.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção que contém todas as exportações que correspondem à condição especificada.
